msgid "The I2P Client Protocol (I2CP) enables external applications (clients) to communicate with I2P over single TCP socket, by default using port 7654. For more information, see the <a href=https://geti2p.net/en/docs/protocol/i2cp class='sitelink external' target=_blank rel=noreferrer>online documentation</a>."
