msgid "A fork of the <a href=http://www.klomp.org/snark/ class='sitelink external' target=_blank rel=noreferrer>Snark BitTorrent client</a> refactored for use on the I2P network. Usually supplied as part of the default suite of applications with Java I2P, and also available as a <a href=http://skank.i2p/#download class=sitelink target=_blank rel=noreferrer>standalone Java application</a>."
