msgid "The act of contributing to the network by permitting other routers to build tunnels using your router in a tunnel chain. At least 12KB/s upstream bandwidth (network share) is required to be allocated in order to enable participation. Note that firewalled routers will be limited in how much they contribute to participation, and a router designated as Hidden will not participate at all."
