msgid "If you're experiencing issues with running I2P+, the following information may help identify and resolve the problem:"
msgstr "∆Źg…ôr I2P+ istehsalńĪ il…ô bańülńĪ probleml…ôrl…ô √ľzl…ôŇüirsinizs…ô, aŇüańüńĪdakńĪ m…ôlumatlar m…ôs…ôl…ôni m√ľ…ôyy…ôn etm…ôk v…ô h…ôll etm…ôy…ô k√∂m…ôk ed…ô bil…ôr:"

msgid "Be Patient!"
