msgid "I2P+ functions best when you can accurately reflect the speed of your network connection in the <a href=/config>bandwidth configuration section</a>. By default I2P+ is configured with some fairly conservative values that will not suit many use cases, so please take time to review these settings and correct where necessary. The more bandwidth you allocate, <i>specifically</i> upstream bandwidth, the more you will benefit from the network."
msgstr "Dońüru Ňü…ôb…ôk…ô bańülantńĪsńĪnńĪn s√ľr…ôtini <a href=/config>band geniŇüliyi konfiqurasiya b√∂lm…ôsind…ô</a> d√ľzg√ľn Ňü…ôkild…ô t…ôqdim etdiyiniz zaman I2P+ …ôn yaxŇüńĪ iŇül…ôy…ôr. I2P+ t…ôxmin…ôn istifad…ô√ßi √ßeŇüidl…ôri il…ô uyńüun g…ôlm…ôy…ôn m√ľs…ôlman q…ôrarlarńĪ il…ô t…ônziml…ônir, bu s…ôb…ôbd…ôn bu t…ônziml…ôm…ôl…ôri √∂hd…ôsind…ôn g…ôl…ôn v…ô d√ľz…ôltm…ôk √ľ√ß√ľn zaman ayńĪrńĪn. Band geniŇüliyi ayńĪrńĪmńĪ n…ô q…ôd…ôr √ßox olarsa, x√ľsus…ôn yuxarńĪ axńĪn geniŇüliyi, Ňü…ôb…ôk…ôd…ôn √ßox fayda g√∂r…ôc…ôksiniz."

msgid "Firewalls, Modems &amp; Routers"
msgstr "YanńüńĪn divarlarńĪ, modeml…ôr &amp; Routerl…ôr"

msgid "Where possible, please ensure I2P+/Java is allowed bi-directional port access from the internet by configuring your modem/router/pc firewall accordingly. If you're behind a prohibitive firewall but have unrestricted outbound access, I2P+ can still function; you can turn off inbound access and rely on <a href=http://i2p-projekt.i2p/udp.html target=_blank rel=noreferrer class=sitelink>SSU IP Address Detection</a> (<a href=https://wikipedia.org/wiki/Hole_punching target=_blank rel=noreferrer class='sitelink external'>firewall hole punching</a>) to connect you to the network, and your network status in the side panel will indicate \"Status: Firewalled\". For optimal performance, please ensure I2P's <a href=/confignet#udpconfig>external port</a> is visible from the internet (see below for more information)."
msgstr "Jahada m√ľmk√ľn olan yerl…ôrd…ô, I2P+/Java proqramńĪna ńįnternetd…ôn h…ôr iki t…ôr…ôfli porta √ßńĪxma icaz…ôsi verm…ôk √ľ√ß√ľn modem / y√∂nl…ôndirici / PC s√ľng…ôrinizi uyńüun Ňü…ôkild…ô konfiqurasiya etm…ôy…ô …ômin olun. ∆Źg…ôr m…ôhdudlaŇüdńĪrńĪlmńĪŇü bir s√ľng…ôr ardńĪcńĪlńĪndasńĪnńĪzsa, lakin s…ôrb…ôst √ßńĪxńĪŇüa maliksinizs…ô, I2P+ h…ôl…ô d…ô iŇül…ôy…ô bil…ôr; g…ôl…ôn m√ľraci…ôti s√∂nd√ľr…ô bil…ôrsiniz v…ô Ňü…ôb…ôk…ôy…ô qoŇüulmaq √ľ√ß√ľn <a href=http://i2p-projekt.i2p/udp.html target=_blank rel=noreferrer class=sitelink>SSU IP √únvanńĪnńĪ AŇükar Etme</a> (<a href=https://wikipedia.org/wiki/Hole_punching target=_blank rel=noreferrer class='sitelink external'>s√ľng…ô yorńüanńĪ</a>) √ľz…ôrind…ô se√ßim ed…ô bil…ôrsiniz network, v…ô yan panelinizd…ôki Ňü…ôb…ôk…ô v…ôziyy…ôti \"Status: Firewalled\" g√∂st…ôril…ôc…ôk. ∆Źn yaxŇüńĪ performans √ľ√ß√ľn, I2P'nin <a href=/confignet#udpconfig>Ňü…ôb…ôk…ôniq aparacńĪ portu</a> internetd…ôn g√∂r√ľn…ô bil…ôr olmalńĪdńĪr (daha √ßox m…ôlumat √ľ√ß√ľn aŇüańüńĪya baxńĪn)."

msgid "Check Your Proxy Settings"
msgstr "Proksi AyarlarńĪnńĪzńĪ YoxlayńĪn"

msgid "If you cannot see any websites at all (not even <a href=http://i2p-projekt.i2p/ target=_blank rel=noreferrer>i2p-projekt.i2p</a>), make sure your browser's proxy is set to access http traffic (<i>not</i> https, <i>not</i> socks) via <code>127.0.0.1 port 4444</code>. If you need some help, there's <a href=https://geti2p.net/en/about/browser-config target=_blank rel=noreferrer class='sitelink external'>a guide</a> to configuring your browser for I2P use."
