msgid "<a href=/logs>Logs</a> may help resolve a problem. You may wish to paste excerpts in a <a href=http://i2pforum.i2p/ target=_blank rel=noreferrer>forum</a> for help, or perhaps <a href=http://cake.i2p/pastebin/ target=_blank rel=noreferrer class='sitelink external'>paste</a> it instead and reference the link on IRC for help."
