msgid "By default, I2P is supplied with a webserver to host your own anonymized website (traditionally referred to as an <i>eepsite</i>). Both the site and the I2P Router Console are running on a streamlined version of <a href='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jetty_(web_server)' target=_blank rel=noreferrer class='sitelink external'>Jetty</a>, customized for I2P."
