msgid "Directory listings (sometimes referred to as virtual directories) are enabled by default, so you can host files from a sub-directory of <code>docroot</code> without providing a page with links to the files. You can also serve content that exists outside of <code>docroot</code> by using a <a href=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Symbolic_link target=_blank rel=noreferrer class='sitelink external'>symbolic link</a> to the desired directory."
