msgid "In order to provide the best experience for visitors to your site, there are various additional steps you may wish to consider once your site is up and running:"
msgstr "SaytńĪnńĪzńĪn ziyar…ôt√ßil…ôri √ľ√ß√ľn …ôn yaxŇüńĪ t…ôcr√ľb…ôni t…ômin etm…ôk √ľ√ß√ľn saytńĪnńĪz iŇü…ô salńĪndńĪqdan sonra n…ôz…ôrd…ôn ke√ßirm…ôk ist…ôdiyiniz m√ľxt…ôlif …ôlav…ô addńĪmlar var:"

msgid "Optimize your images"
msgstr "Ňě…ôkill…ôrinizi optimallaŇüdńĪrńĪn"

msgid "If you want your site to feel responsive, image compression is essential when hosting large images. Using a service like <a href=https://tinypng.com/ target=_blank class='sitelink external'>tinypng.com</a> to compress your png and jpeg images will often result in much smaller files with minimal loss of quality. In some situations the webp format can best jpegs, generating smaller files with approximately the same or better visual fidelity, and has wide browser support. Also consider using svgs instead of bitmaps for icons and illustrations - they're often smaller than the equivalent bitmap file (run them through a service like <a href=https://vecta.io/nano target=_blank class='sitelink external'>Nano SVG Optimizer</a> to remove unneeded cruft), scale without loss of quality, and can be gzipped by your webserver."
msgstr "∆Źg…ôr √∂z saytńĪnńĪzńĪn daha √ß…ôyird…ô olduńüunu hiss etm…ôk ist…ôyirsinizs…ô, b√∂y√ľk Ňü…ôkill…ôri yerl…ôŇüdirdiyiniz zaman Ňü…ôkil sńĪxńĪŇüdńĪrmasńĪ …ôsas olduqda vacibdir. PNG v…ô JPEG Ňü…ôkill…ôrinizi sńĪxńĪŇüdńĪrma xidm…ôtl…ôrind…ôn istifad…ô etm…ôk (m…ôs…ôl…ôn, <a href=https://tinypng.com/ target=_blank class='sitelink external'>tinypng.com</a>) genellikl…ô daha ki√ßik fayllara (azad…ôsiz keyfiyy…ôt itkisind…ôn asńĪlńĪ olaraq) s…ôb…ôb ola bil…ôr. B…ôzi hallarda, webp formatńĪ yantanńĪn √ľst√ľn qarŇüńĪsńĪnńĪ ala bil…ôr, yaxŇüńĪlaŇüan dildirsizlikl…ô daha ki√ßik fayllar yaradńĪr v…ô geniŇü brauzer d…ôst…ôyi il…ô t…ômin edilir. H…ôm√ßinin, ikonlar v…ô t…ôsvirl…ôr √ľ√ß√ľn bitmaps fayllarńĪn yerin…ô svgl…ôri istifad…ô etm…ôyi d√ľŇü√ľn√ľn ‚Äď onlar adilikd…ôn daha ki√ßik olurlar (<a href=https://vecta.io/nano target=_blank class='sitelink external'>Nano SVG Optimizer</a> kimil…ôrind…ôn ke√ßirin unudulmuŇü l…ôŇüdlik elementl…ôrini silm…ôk √ľ√ß√ľn), adilik itkil…ôri olmadan √ßapalarlar, v…ô veb serveriniz t…ôr…ôfind…ôn gzip edil…ô bil…ôrl…ôr."

msgid "Use separate files for multi-use assets"
msgstr "√áoxlu istifad…ô √ľ√ß√ľn f…ôrqli fayllar istifad…ô edin"

msgid "Wherever possible, assets that are used repeatedly on your site should be loaded from an external file and not inlined. If you're using the same CSS on several pages, create a separate css file and load that in the <code>&lt;head&gt;</code> section of your pages. This will make styling updates to your site easier to manage, and will also allow the file to be cached in the visitor's browser, resulting in less bandwidth demands on your webserver and faster page loads for your visitors."
msgstr "SaytńĪnńĪzda t…ôkrarlanan Ňü…ôb…ôk…ô hiss…ôl…ôri varsa, m√ľmk√ľns…ô, onlarńĪ bir xarici fayldan y√ľkl…ôm…ôk v…ô sńĪradan yaratmaq daha yaxŇüńĪdńĪr. Bir ne√ß…ô s…ôhif…ôd…ô eyni CSS istifad…ô edirsinizs…ô, m√ľst…ôqil bir css faylńĪ yaradńĪn v…ô onu s…ôhif…ôl…ôrinizin <code>&lt;head&gt;</code> hiss…ôsind…ô y√ľkl…ôyin. Bu, saytńĪnńĪzńĪn √ľslubunu idar…ô etm…ôk √ľ√ß√ľn daha asan yenil…ôm…ôl…ôr ed…ôc…ôk v…ô h…ôm√ßinin faylńĪn t…ôr…ôfdaŇüńĪn brauzerind…ô ke√ßilm…ôsin…ô imkan ver…ôc…ôkdir, bu da veb serverinizin bant geniŇüliyind…ôn daha az istifad…ô etm…ôyiniz…ô v…ô ziyar…ôt√ßil…ôriniz…ô daha s√ľr…ôtli s…ôhif…ô y√ľkl…ônm…ôsin…ô s…ôb…ôb ola bil…ôr."

msgid "Consider using a backend cache"
msgstr "Arxa u√ßdavaranńĪn istifad…ôsini n…ôz…ôr…ô alńĪn"

msgid "If you're running a dynamic site handling a large number of concurrent users, content caching can often improve the time taken to deliver pages. For content that rapidly changes, a <a href=https://blog.stackpath.com/glossary-micro-caching/ target=_blank class='sitelink external'>micro-caching strategy</a> may still yield some benefits. The <a href=https://www.nginx.com/ target=_blank class='sitelink external'>Nginx webserver</a> provides a competent caching sub-system, or for a more heavy-weight solution, have a look at <a href=https://varnish-cache.org/ target=_blank class='sitelink external'>Varnish</a>."
msgstr "∆Źg…ôr bir √ßox m√ľxt…ôlif istifad…ô√ßi idar…ô olunan dinamik bir sayt iŇül…ôdirsinizs…ô, m…ôzmunu √∂nbellekl…ôm…ô vaxt itirm…ônin azalmasńĪna …ôlav…ô kimi t…ômin ed…ô bil…ôr. M…ôrh…ôl…ôli d…ôyiŇü…ôn m…ôzmun √ľ√ß√ľn <a href=https://blog.stackpath.com/glossary-micro-caching/ target=_blank class='sitelink external'>mikro-√∂nbellekl…ôm…ô strategiyasńĪ</a> h…ôl…ô d…ô b…ôzi faydalar ver…ô bil…ôr. <a href=https://www.nginx.com/ target=_blank class='sitelink external'>Nginx veb-server</a> yaxŇüńĪ bir √∂nbellekl…ôm…ô alt sistemi t…ôklif edir v…ô daha √ß…ôtindir bir h…ôll √ľ√ß√ľn <a href=https://varnish-cache.org/ target=_blank class='sitelink external'>Varnish</a>…ô d…ô n…ôz…ôr salsaq."

msgid "Using an alternative webserver"
msgstr "Alternativ veb-server istifad…ôsi"

msgid "To configure an alternative webserver for use on I2P, you can either use the existing webserver tunnel and <a href=/configclients>disable the default webserver</a> from running, or create a new HTTP Server tunnel in the <a href=/i2ptunnelmgr>Tunnel Manager</a>. Ensure that the webserver's <i>listening port</i> is also configured in the Tunnel Manager settings. For example, if your webserver is listening by default on address 127.0.0.1 port 80, you'd also need to ensure that the <i>Target port</i> in the Tunnel Manager settings page for the service is also configured to port 80."
msgstr "I2P-d…ô alternativ bir veb-serveri konfiqurasiya etm…ôk √ľ√ß√ľn, m√∂vcud veb-serverin t√ľnell…ôrind…ôn istifad…ô ed…ô v…ô ya yeni bir HTTP Server t√ľn…ôlini <a href=/configclients>bucańüńĪndan qaldńĪra bil…ôrsiniz. gediŇüat almanańüńĪnńĪn iŇül…ônm…ôsini deaktivl…ôŇüdirm…ôk √ľ√ß√ľn, yaxud <a href=/i2ptunnelmgr>T√ľnell…ôr meneceri</a>-d…ô yeni bir HTTP Server t√ľr…ôsi yaradńĪla bil…ôr. Veb serverin <i> dinl…ônm…ô ha√ßńĪ</i> ayrńĪca T√ľnell…ôr Meneceri ayarlarńĪnda konfiqurasiya edilsin. M…ôs…ôl…ôn, ehtimal ed…ôk ki, veb serveriniz 127.0.0.1 √ľnvanńĪnda 80 portunda dinl…ônir, o zaman xidm…ôt √ľ√ß√ľn T√ľnell…ôr Menecerind…ôki <i>H…ôd…ôf port</i>nun konfiqurasiya edildiyin…ô d…ô …ômin olmalńĪsńĪnńĪz oldiqda port 80 d…ôdir."

msgid "To preserve anonymity, make sure that the webserver is not publicly available outside of the I2P network, which is normally achieved by configuring the webserver to listen on localhost (127.0.0.1) rather than all interfaces (0.0.0.0)."
